"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#how-"
"can-i-enable-the-wordpress-rest-api-in-my-website"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#how-"
"can-i-enable-the-wordpress-rest-api-in-my-website"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:666
msgid ""
"Response from the server is malformed. This indicates, for example, that "
"another plugin is manipulating the response. In the following, you find the "
